This paper is about object detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses domain adaptation, which is a common problem in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed framework is designed to be resilient to noise in the data, which is a common problem in robotics (cs.RO) and computer security (cs.CR).
